Package org.dapper.server

A package for the Dapper server.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientState
    The Dapper server-side client state that stores information on a per-client basis, but forwards all events on to a ServerProcessor instance.
    Server
    The Dapper server class.
    ServerLogic
    A class that houses the Dapper server logic.
    ServerProcessor
    The Dapper server processor.
    ServerProcessor.FlowBuildRequest
    A container class for requesting that a Flow be built.
